<br>
I'd say that if you're getting close to 51 (49), then it's probably not worth the camp.  You're probably better off leveling to 51 + 3 AA's (and you'd level pretty quickly and be able to get those AA's at the Dryads, assuming that such posts haven't crowded the Dryads so much that they're perma-camped (if so, do Seafury Cyclops' or any of the many others suggested in these forums)).<br>
<br>
Now if you're able to get JBoots in the low 40's, then woot!  It's probably the single best addition to the solo mage's arsenal available, until run3 makes it mostly redundant.  Bought sow potions are a good substitute, assuming that you can replenish the ~10p/shot that it costs (as you can, easily, hunting hill giants in Rathe).  But unlike JBoots sow potions can't be activated while running (escaping).<br>
<br>
